===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|poisoun}}, {{m|enm|poyson}}, {{m|enm|poysone}}, {{m|enm|puyson}}, {{m|enm|puisun}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|puison}}, {{m|fro|poison}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|pōtio|pōtio, pōtiōnis|drink, a draught, a poisonous draught, a potion}}, from {{m|la|poto|pōtō|to drink}}. See also {{m|en|potion}} and {{m|en|potable}}.

